unctuation">=</span> &#x27;0f3cbb44-f199-4d34-ade9-<span class="number">1545</span>c<span class="number">097264</span>8&#x27;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>复制cookie中token的值</p><p>然后在<a href="https://www.jwt.io/%E4%B8%AD%E6%9E%84%E9%80%A0admin%E7%9A%84token">https://www.jwt.io/中构造admin的token</a></p><p>注：</p><figure class="highlight mipsasm"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">JWT </span>Decoder</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">JWT </span>Encoder</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>存在这俩板块</p><p>随后得到flag</p><h1 id="3-We-will-rockyou"><a href="#3-We-will-rockyou" class="headerlink" title="3.We_will_rockyou"></a>3.We_will_rockyou</h1><p>附件中发现</p><figure class="highlight isbl"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="variable"><span class="keyword">if</span></span> <span class="variable">__name__</span> == <span class="string">&#x27;__main__&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable">admin_id</span> = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable">admin_username</span> = <span class="string">&#x27;admin123&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="variable">admin_password</span> = <span class="function"><span class="title">str</span>(<span class="variable">uuid.uuid4</span>())</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>做fuzz测试知道有rockyou字典</p><p>插入使用</p><p>测出密码：chelsea</p><p>登入尝试执行命令</p><p>存在waf</p><p>附件中白名单</p><figure class="highlight ini"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">SAFE_COMMANDS</span> = [<span class="string">&#x27;ls&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;pwd&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;whoami&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;dir&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;more&#x27;</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>利用more读取more &#x2F;flag</p><p>Output</p><figure class="highlight maxima"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">PCTF&#123;f805b6d0-d026-<span class="number">41b0</span>-<span class="number">9279</span>-937feee61c16&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id="4-神秘商店"><a href="#4-神秘商店" class="headerlink" title="4.神秘商店"></a>4.神秘商店</h1><p>登录admin</p><p>利用全角来注册登录</p><p>后端代码有转换，全角能够绕过后端对admin的检测，然后把全角admin识别成正常的admin，造成覆盖注册，修改admin密码</p><p>注册admin，其中n为全角</p><p>利用整数溢出4294967246到50，购买flag</p><h1 id="5-php-with-md5"><a href="#5-php-with-md5" class="headerlink" title="5.php_with_md5"></a>5.php_with_md5</h1><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br></pre></td